    <!-- Strings related to Help -->

    <string name="help_page_intro">This app will lead you to the place you need. At any point of time it will show you the direction and
        the distance to reach your destination. All you need is:\n
        - compass sensor in your device\n
        - enabled location service\n
        - defined destination\n\n
    There are several ways to define the destination.
    </string>

    <string name="help_text_version">Version: </string>

    <string name="help_text_section1">You can enter the bearing and the distance to your target from your current location. The app will do the rest.
    </string>

    <string name="help_text_section2">You can also enter the absolute coordinates of your destination. The app will show you where to go (and how far)
        once the GPS location has been obtained. Any coordinates format can be used.
    </string>

    <string name="help_text_section3">The app can also remember your current location and show how to return wherever you go. This mode can be useful
        for example to remember the location of your car before you enter the dense forest.
    </string>

    <string name="help_text_section4">You can save your current or target location and load it later at any time to proceed your movement or to return to the place you have already been.
    </string>

